{"id": 1741, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都从哪些细节感知一部影视剧的品质？", "description": "别再说《深夜食堂》被泡面毁了，集合了各种反人类逻辑和让人感觉活在 2005 年的陈年老梗，这么说太冤枉泡面一个人了。", "record_count": 4183, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170614103105n3mWTpIugdvj71eS.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-14T02:36:26Z", "options": [{"id": 212736, "content": "看色调一眼足以决定应否追剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 381, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346805}, {"id": 212737, "content": "没有小鲜肉", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 424564}, {"id": 212993, "content": "是否有逻辑，场景是否和故事有融入感，台词是否自然，演员和人物设定是否匹配", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745623}, {"id": 212738, "content": "看路人演的好不好就行啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 804076}, {"id": 212994, "content": "没上过快乐大本营", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 824654}, {"id": 212739, "content": "不是中国出的", "image": null, "praise_count": 126, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 43355}, {"id": 212995, "content": "尬到厌食……只求接地气。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055340}, {"id": 212740, "content": "这么热？我路过！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051583}, {"id": 212996, "content": "滤镜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 542427}, {"id": 212741, "content": "看完两集我去用三江水洗洗眼睛，冲冲耳朵。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 9787}, {"id": 212997, "content": "一般从主角出场到第二集半中间，基本可定该剧是否值得追", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818331}, {"id": 214277, "content": "不要让我去猜通过你的演技 你要表达什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058389}, {"id": 212742, "content": "尊重一下观众的智商", "image": null, "praise_count": 610, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054903}, {"id": 212998, "content": "就不能找个地方拍么 在棚里拍太假了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829209}, {"id": 212743, "content": "方便面以后是没法吃了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050309}, {"id": 212999, "content": "三观正", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046593}, {"id": 214023, "content": "哭戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016973}, {"id": 213000, "content": "只要是某小鲜肉担纲的就可以直接pass了╮(╯_╰)╭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169698}, {"id": 212745, "content": "表演不要太用力，平淡如水却走心", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490748}, {"id": 213001, "content": "看这剧是不是拿观众当弱智", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 362670}, {"id": 214025, "content": "一哭二闹三上吊——过于情绪化的剧就不是高明的剧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051505}, {"id": 212746, "content": "角色发型。抹好发胶打鬼子的全换台", "image": null, "praise_count": 109, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535937}, {"id": 213002, "content": "大大方方卖广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958078}, {"id": 213514, "content": "40多集广告怎么了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056207}, {"id": 212747, "content": "符合逻辑", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054912}, {"id": 213003, "content": "出门时记得关，离开自行车记得锁！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055374}, {"id": 212748, "content": "声音！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834136}, {"id": 212749, "content": "服化道是基本，台词见真章", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015291}, {"id": 213005, "content": "日剧原版的本身是浓浓的烟火味，现在被改编的太有言情剧的气质，太过风尘。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991147}, {"id": 212750, "content": "古装衣服不要太“时尚” 头发胡子不要那么“整齐”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011007}, {"id": 213006, "content": "广东如何一个出名的大排档都比这部剧更具良心和接地气。更具人文关怀。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 798369}, {"id": 213518, "content": "太干净！人脸都像陶瓷一般完美无瑕的，都不是好电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1032375}, {"id": 212751, "content": "台词", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001983}, {"id": 213007, "content": "符合情节人物设计的小细节", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055376}, {"id": 213775, "content": "最受不了黄磊的那身衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056710}, {"id": 216335, "content": "日式温馨美式酷炫韩式浪漫", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056538}, {"id": 212752, "content": "台词 布景 道具", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001376}, {"id": 213008, "content": "光线质感是不是电视节目质感", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 12364}, {"id": 215824, "content": "配音对不上嘴形", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1060581}, {"id": 216592, "content": "翻拍倒是没什么，但是请用点心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064570}, {"id": 212753, "content": "群演的表现", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630956}, {"id": 213009, "content": "服装", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055378}, {"id": 214545, "content": "瞪眼撅嘴就是全部演技～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1059357}, {"id": 212754, "content": "剧情干净流畅有逻辑", "image": null, "praise_count": 93, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034555}, {"id": 213010, "content": "有本事别老翻拍，拍出点自己的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930505}, {"id": 212755, "content": "三观正", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011544}, {"id": 213011, "content": "光线的变化", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519309}, {"id": 212756, "content": "演员的动作神情，特别是一些微小的变化", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051021}, {"id": 213012, "content": "演技和剧情证明一切", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051232}, {"id": 215316, "content": "插曲都好听", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113262}]}